metadata.description: Based on the smash-hit Instagram account, But Like Maybe? is a new comic book about life and stuff. A bible for millennials (and those trying to understand them), BLM examines the complicated world of selfies, brunch, hangovers, love, rejection, and over-analyzing everything. Cheers to the guys you pretend not to stalk and the carbs you pretend not to eat. BLM is vulnerable so you don't have to be! The voice of a generation...But Like Maybe?
metadata.name: But Like Maybe?
